        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-2",
        "text": "Or that we&apos;d have to say Goodbye to you so fast",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -27.827,
          "y_px": -222.356
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-3",
        "text": "And that you haven&apos;t really gone away",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -18.077,
          "y_px": -123.841
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "We didn&apos;t know that day would be our last",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -94.846,
          "y_px": -243.913
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "I know you&apos;re watching over me, I talk to you everyday",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -1.767,
          "y_px": 33.281
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-6",
        "text": "To those memories I&apos;ll hold on tight",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -20.796,
          "y_px": 5.002
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-7",
        "text": "I miss you so much my Son, my heart is torn apart",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -2.393,
          "y_px": 97.472
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "I believe you see my soul with every word I say",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -12.499,
          "y_px": 70.653
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "To hear your voice and to see your face again",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -22.846,
          "y_px": -174.288
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "We miss you so much Jimmy, our hearts are just aching",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -8.231,
          "y_px": -201.99
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "I pray, LORD, please tell us we&apos;re only dreamin&apos;",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -35.752,
          "y_px": -145.221
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "God must&apos;ve just needed to bring you Home",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -24.018,
          "y_px": -101.421
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "His Angels must be rejoicing",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -12.778,
          "y_px": -78.229
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "That my Big Brother is with them in Heaven today",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -1.043,
          "y_px": -50.225
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "All the WONDERFUL times, we had so MANY together",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 10.151,
          "y_px": -22.992
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "Around the Throne tonight",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -42.553,
          "y_px": 269.221
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "We&apos;ll wait for our Chariot to swing low to the ground",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -7.02,
          "y_px": 292.656
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "Well God took the most precious one I know",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -33.612,
          "y_px": 215.648
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "In a world where heros come and go",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -5.604,
          "y_px": 188.408
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "Even with miles between us you always knew when to call",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 7.844,
          "y_px": 120.654
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-22",
        "text": "I just can&apos;t accept you&apos;re gone Son, it just doesn&apos;t feel right",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -0.403,
          "y_px": 142.743
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "You&apos;re in our hearts til we see you again on that Great Day",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0.137,
          "y_px": 339.501
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-24",
        "text": "And take us home to see you again",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 19
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -9.013,
